00:17:15.677 --> 00:17:18.277
Wanita merah.

288
00:17:22.177 --> 00:17:23.377
Wanita merah?

289
00:17:23.877 --> 00:17:25.377
Tidak mungkin, bukan?

290
00:17:25.377 --> 00:17:28.277
Kematiannya telah dikonfirmasi.

291
00:17:28.277 --> 00:17:29.877
Tapi...

292
00:17:29.877 --> 00:17:31.577
Setelah mati lampu,

293
